<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include('./partials/head.ejs') %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('./partials/header.ejs') %>
    <main>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="page-title uppercase">
          <h1>site information</h1>
        </div>
        <h2 class="page-section-title">overview</h2>
        <ul class="info-ul">
          <li>
            This app is a private neighborhood message board intended to help neighbors share information in timely fashion.
          </li>
          <li>
            Access is limited to people who live in the 
            <span class="red-letter">C</span>apital
            <span class="red-letter">A</span>rea
            <span class="red-letter">N</span>eigborhood. Non-neighborhood residents may be allowed to participate on an ad hoc basis as <span class="italic">guests</span>, but will not be given full <span class="italic">member</span> status, which is limited to trusted neighbors active in <span class="red-letter">C.A.N.</span> organization.
          </li>
          <li>
            This app is not a commercial product and is provided as-is for
            community use.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <br />
        <h2 class="page-section-title">how to use</h2>
        <ul class="info-ul">
          <li>
            Create an account using accurate information so your identity can be
            verified.
          </li>
          <li>Browse and post messages by existing topics.</li>
          <li>
            Use the app for local announcements, questions, and relevant updates
            by topic only.
          </li>
          <li>
            Messages are temporary and will automatically expire after a set
            period days (see below).
          </li>
        </ul>
        <br />
        <h2 class="page-section-title">how to send messages</h2>
        <ul class="info-ul">
          <li>
            Sign up to join first, then log in.
          </li>
          <li>Once logged in, go to the message board and
            select the most relevant topic for your message.
          </li>
          <li>Post a message based on something relevant that you wish to share with your neighbors (see Community Guidelines below).
          </li>
        </ul>
        <br />
        <h2 class="page-section-title">Community guidelines</h2>
        <ul class="info-ul">
          <li>
            Keep it brief! Write short, clear messages that are relevant to the message board topic.
          </li>
          <li>Assume messages are visible to all users of this app.</li>
          <li>Avoid sharing sensitive personal information.</li>
          <li>
            Be respectful of others. Do not harass, threaten, or impersonate
            others.
          </li>
          <li>
            Do not post false, misleading, or intentionally harmful information.
          </li>
          <li>Use common sense—this is a shared community space for neighbors.</li>
          <li>Messages may be removed if they violate any community guidelines.</li>
        </ul>
        <br />
        <h2 class="page-section-title">message expiration</h2>
        <ul class="info-ul">
          <li>
            All messages automatically expire and are deleted after a fixed
            period of time. All messages are tagged with an expiration date.
          </li>
          <li>Expired messages cannot be recovered. This helps keep information current and reduces long-term data
            retention.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <br />
        <h2 class="page-section-title">license information</h2>
        <ul class="info-ul">
          <li>
            This app uses the
            <a class="app-link" href="https://mit-license.org/">MIT License</a>.
          </li>
          <li>
            The license applies to the app’s source code, not user-generated
            content.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <br />
        <h2 class="page-section-title">terms & conditions</h2>
        <ul class="info-ul">
          <li>
            By using this app, you agree to these terms and all posted
            guidelines.
          </li>
          <li>You are responsible for the content you post.</li>
          <li>
            The app owner is not responsible for user-generated content or
            actions taken based on it.
          </li>
          <li>Access may be suspended or revoked at any time for misuse.</li>
          <li>The app may change, pause, or shut down without notice.</li>
        </ul>
        <br />
        <h2 class="page-section-title">privacy policy</h2>
        <ul class="info-ul">
          <li>
            Basic personal information is collected to verify neighborhood
            membership.
          </li>
          <li>
            Data is used only for internal verification and community purposes.
          </li>
          <li>Your information is not sold or shared with third parties.</li>
          <li>
            Reasonable steps are taken to keep data secure, but no system is
            guaranteed.
          </li>
          <li>You may request correction or removal of your data.</li>
        </ul>
        <br />
        <h2 class="page-section-title">attributions</h2>
        <ul class="info-ul">
          <li>Emoji naming based off of JSON file created by <a class="app-link" href="https://github.com/BehrouzSohrabi/Emoji/blob/main/emoji-list-categories.json?h=1">Behrouz Sohrabi</a></li>
        </ul>
        <br />
      </div>
    </main>
    <%- include('./partials/modal-root.ejs') %>
    <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>
  </body>
</html>
